<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 22:05:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈马斯播放以色列在加沙被扣为人质的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/hamas-airs-video-of-israeli-held-hostage-in-gaza-captivity/0000018f-68a1-ddc4-a79f-7ca9552e0000</link><description>以色列军方认为 Nadav Poplewell 的视频很可能是过时的，他的兄弟于 10 月 7 日被杀</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 17:25:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/hamas-airs-video-of-israeli-held-hostage-in-gaza-captivity/0000018f-68a1-ddc4-a79f-7ca9552e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数万人抗议政府，警方与人质家人发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/police-clash-with-hostages-families-as-tens-of-thousands-protest-govt-across-israel/0000018f-6820-de93-a1af-7c28f1580000</link><description>“内塔尼亚胡正在带领以色列国彻底失败。埃纳夫·赞高克（Einav Zangauker）的儿子马坦（Matan）被关押在加沙，他呼吁以色列部长们停止合作，推翻政府，拯救人质和国家。</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 17:20:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/police-clash-with-hostages-families-as-tens-of-thousands-protest-govt-across-israel/0000018f-6820-de93-a1af-7c28f1580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 218 天：以色列国防军称 30 万人从拉法撤离至人道主义区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-day-218-idf-says-300-000-evacuated-from-rafah-to-humanitarian-zone/0000018f-6890-d284-adaf-7cfc7dce0000</link><description>以色列国防军：30 万人从加沙拉法撤离 ■ 拜登政府：“合理评估”以色列在“不符合”国际人道主义法的情况下使用了美国提供的武器，但没有给出结论性声明，称缺乏核实事件的信息 ■ 哈马斯的言论以色列人质视频 ■ 南非要求国际法院下令以色列从拉法撤军 ■ 战争进入 218 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 17:19:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-day-218-idf-says-300-000-evacuated-from-rafah-to-humanitarian-zone/0000018f-6890-d284-adaf-7cfc7dce0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列欧洲电视网选手在决赛中欢呼雀跃；马尔默数千人抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/eurovision-reaches-its-grand-final-as-gaza-war-tensions-steal-the-spotlight/0000018f-683a-de93-a1af-7c3afe010000</link><description>数千人在马尔默游行，抗议以色列歌手伊登·戈兰的参与并要求加沙停火；警方驱散了体育场外的数十名抗议者；在芬兰，数十名抗议者冲进公共广播公司总部，要求其因以色列的参与而退出歌曲比赛</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 15:56:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/eurovision-reaches-its-grand-final-as-gaza-war-tensions-steal-the-spotlight/0000018f-683a-de93-a1af-7c3afe010000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队返回贾巴利亚，指责哈马斯重组缺乏外交程序</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-prepares-for-north-gaza-combat-accuses-hamas-regrouping-on-lack-of-diplomatic-process/0000018f-67df-d9a0-a38f-efff88f30000</link><description>以色列军队正在加沙城北部的贾巴利亚做好战斗准备，去年 12 月，以色列声称哈马斯营已清除该地区。 15万居民被号召南下疏散</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 14:21:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-prepares-for-north-gaza-combat-accuses-hamas-regrouping-on-lack-of-diplomatic-process/0000018f-67df-d9a0-a38f-efff88f30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，在以色列行动之前，有30万人从加沙南部的拉法撤离到人道主义区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-300-000-people-evacuated-rafah-to-humanitarian-zone-ahead-of-israeli-operation/0000018f-66a6-de93-a1af-7eae4ee70000</link><description>以色列国防军表示摧毁了哈马斯在加沙北部的军事能力几个月后，以色列军队正在重新部署到该地区，以遏制哈马斯营的重组。军队还宣布对加沙南部拉法更多地区下达疏散令</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 09:01:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-300-000-people-evacuated-rafah-to-humanitarian-zone-ahead-of-israeli-operation/0000018f-66a6-de93-a1af-7eae4ee70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军士兵在加沙北部战斗中丧生；以色列对加沙北部发动猛烈轰炸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article-live/france-demands-halting-rafah-op-u-s-hints-at-israels-violations-of-intel-law-in-gaza/0000018f-6570-d284-adaf-757ce3af0000</link><description>德国肖尔茨警告说，对拉法发动地面攻击是不负责任的行为 ■ Alqahera News 报道，埃及拒绝与以色列协调援助物资从拉法过境点进入 ■ 哈马斯发布了以色列人质纳达夫·波普尔韦尔 (Nadav Poplewell) 的视频 ■ 以色列国防军向加沙北部的贾巴利亚部署部队，称哈马斯已经在该地区进行重组 ■ 以色列国防军称 30 万加沙人已撤离拉法</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 02:42:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article-live/france-demands-halting-rafah-op-u-s-hints-at-israels-violations-of-intel-law-in-gaza/0000018f-6570-d284-adaf-757ce3af0000</guid></item><item><title>一名巴勒斯坦青少年骑着摩托车站在街上，被以色列军队开枪打死。</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-05-11/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-palestinian-teen-was-standing-on-the-street-when-israeli-troops-shot-him-dead/0000018f-6483-d3cc-a3ff-ee9b74ab0000</link><description>一名男孩站在图尔卡姆街上，看着以色列军队向该市的难民营开进。士兵们从数百米外开枪，其中一颗子弹击中男孩的胸部。 Qais Nasrallah 去世时年仅 14 岁</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 22:24:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-05-11/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-palestinian-teen-was-standing-on-the-street-when-israeli-troops-shot-him-dead/0000018f-6483-d3cc-a3ff-ee9b74ab0000</guid></item><item><title>我的朋友，纳斯鲁拉的最大粉丝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/my-friend-nasrallahs-biggest-fan/0000018f-6409-d9a0-a38f-ec2f0d170000</link><description>从我们在伦敦见面的那一刻起，兰达拉和我几乎形影不离。我们有很多共同点。但她来自黎巴嫩，我来自以色列，最终她迷上了激进的伊斯兰教</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 21:56:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/my-friend-nasrallahs-biggest-fan/0000018f-6409-d9a0-a38f-ec2f0d170000</guid></item><item><title>美国称“合理评估”以色列在加沙违反国际法，但不会停止武器援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-says-reasonable-to-assess-israel-violated-international-law-but-wont-halt-arms-aid/0000018f-645a-d8a0-a3df-7e7aaffe0000</link><description>政府声称以色列没有阻碍人道主义援助的提供 — — 甚至被称为“持续评估” — — 很可能是报告中最具争议的内容，肯定会受到各个政治派别的严厉批评</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 21:24:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-says-reasonable-to-assess-israel-violated-international-law-but-wont-halt-arms-aid/0000018f-645a-d8a0-a3df-7e7aaffe0000</guid></item><item><title>这种大屠杀叙事迫使以色列人接受更少的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/this-holocaust-narrative-forces-israelis-to-settle-for-less/0000018f-5f23-d82e-a5df-7f33623f0000</link><description>不断提醒我们，犹太人民在大屠杀后奋起反抗，给予我们在恶劣环境下继续前行的力量。但这也迫使我们用太少的钱凑合</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 19:41:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/this-holocaust-narrative-forces-israelis-to-settle-for-less/0000018f-5f23-d82e-a5df-7f33623f0000</guid></item><item><title>不是反犹太主义者，也不是反犹太复国主义者：更准确的术语是指那些希望以色列消失的抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/anti-zionists-a-more-precise-term-for-pro-palestinian-protesters-who-want-israel-gone/0000018f-63b5-d284-adaf-77fda2890000</link><description>在 Reddit 上，我主要发现了有关 10 月 7 日和加沙战争的有趣且内容丰富的对话。直到一篇文章让我大吃一惊，我无法忍住</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 19:39:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/anti-zionists-a-more-precise-term-for-pro-palestinian-protesters-who-want-israel-gone/0000018f-63b5-d284-adaf-77fda2890000</guid></item><item><title>四名以色列士兵在加沙北部被爆炸装置炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/four-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-explosive-device-in-northern-gaza/0000018f-6398-d8a0-a3df-7bb8dfa90000</link><description>爆炸还造成一名军官和另一名战斗士兵受重伤，爆炸发生时部队正在加沙城南部的 Zeitoun 附近执行任务，而加沙南部的两名士兵则因反坦克火力而受重伤。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 18:24:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/four-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-explosive-device-in-northern-gaza/0000018f-6398-d8a0-a3df-7bb8dfa90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人不应该需要逮捕令来维持人性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israelis-shouldnt-need-arrest-warrants-to-maintain-their-humanity/0000018f-635a-d3cc-a3ff-efda3c9c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 17:41:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israelis-shouldnt-need-arrest-warrants-to-maintain-their-humanity/0000018f-635a-d3cc-a3ff-efda3c9c0000</guid></item><item><title>在拉法，人们在满目疮痍的沙漠中无处可逃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/in-rafah-people-flee-to-nowhere-in-a-desert-of-devastation-and-sand/0000018f-62b5-d8a0-a3df-7ab5e07b0000</link><description>大约 120 万加沙人挤在这座已经遭受毁灭性爆炸和炮击的城市里。他们确信拜登的警告不会阻止像加沙城和汗尤尼斯那样的大规模地面袭击</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 17:12:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/in-rafah-people-flee-to-nowhere-in-a-desert-of-devastation-and-sand/0000018f-62b5-d8a0-a3df-7ab5e07b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 217 天：近东救济工程处称迄今为止已有 11 万人逃离拉法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-217-unrwa-says-110-000-have-fled-rafah-so-far/0000018f-635a-d9a0-a38f-ef7f90650001</link><description>WH：拜登政府尚未就向以色列运送武器做出最终决定 ■ CNN 报道，哈马斯要求停火 12 周，而不是以色列同意的六周 ■ 以色列坦克占领了拉法东部和西部的主要道路 ■ 内塔尼亚胡10 月 7 日称“政府的首要责任是保护人民……而人民却没有得到保护” ■ 这是战争进入 217 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 16:43:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-217-unrwa-says-110-000-have-fled-rafah-so-far/0000018f-635a-d9a0-a38f-ef7f90650001</guid></item><item><title>以色列不是土耳其或沙特阿拉伯，拜登打算保持这种状态</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-isnt-turkey-or-saudi-arabia-and-biden-intends-to-keep-it-this-way/0000018f-6289-d9a0-a38f-eeaf3b620000</link><description>美国总统正试图阻止以色列成为一个被贱民国家，认为自己有义务维持两国之间的历史联盟。以色列领导人似乎完全无视这一使命</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 14:24:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-isnt-turkey-or-saudi-arabia-and-biden-intends-to-keep-it-this-way/0000018f-6289-d9a0-a38f-eeaf3b620000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡承认以色列政府在 10 月 7 日失败：“我对自己和每个人都坚持这一点”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-admits-israeli-government-failed-on-oct-7-i-hold-myself-and-everyone-on-this/0000018f-622c-d8a0-a3df-7a2c011e0000</link><description>以色列总理在接受菲尔·麦格劳博士采访时表示，“政府的首要责任是保护人民，这是最终的全面责任，但人民没有得到保护，我们不得不承认这一点”</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 12:16:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-admits-israeli-government-failed-on-oct-7-i-hold-myself-and-everyone-on-this/0000018f-622c-d8a0-a3df-7a2c011e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的根本冲突正在加沙战争中上演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-foundational-conflict-is-playing-out-in-the-gaza-war/0000018f-61ed-d9a0-a38f-edef3ed90000</link><description>下周，以色列将严肃地庆祝其独立，这是犹太复国主义的胜利，其意义本应得到解决。那么为什么争论仍然存在呢？</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 11:39:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-foundational-conflict-is-playing-out-in-the-gaza-war/0000018f-61ed-d9a0-a38f-edef3ed90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列示威者焚烧近东救济工程处东耶路撒冷大院；据报道“严重”损坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-demonstrators-torch-unrwa-east-jerusalem-compound-extensive-damage-reported/0000018f-61c4-d284-adaf-75fc34820000</link><description>警方表示，犯下这一行为的可能是低于刑事责任年龄的儿童，并表示，随着近东救济工程处要求以色列恢复“适当的安全”，他们将进一步调查；该机构负责人指示关闭该大楼，称其工人的生命处于危险之中</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 09:42:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-demonstrators-torch-unrwa-east-jerusalem-compound-extensive-damage-reported/0000018f-61c4-d284-adaf-75fc34820000</guid></item></channel></rss>